606
00:29:28,010 --> 00:29:28,980
Zigui.

607
00:29:28,980 --> 00:29:31,220
- Scared of pain? Then why learn martial arts?
- Exactly.

608
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:33,530
Because Lord Yin personally
went to Jiangdong and

609
