taking Zigui as his disciple.

610
00:29:34,940 --> 00:29:35,780
Right?

611
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:38,860
I heard the Mu Wei Palace
was just renovated.

612
00:29:38,860 --> 00:29:39,900
