647
00:32:25,770 --> 00:32:26,940
I won't surrender.

648
00:32:28,620 --> 00:32:29,770
I won't surrender.

649
00:32:30,490 --> 00:32:31,330
Keep beating him.

650
00:32:43,740 --> 00:32:44,980
