651
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:45,820
Father.

652
00:32:46,860 --> 00:32:47,700
Mother.

653
00:32:50,290 --> 00:32:51,220
It hurts.

654
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:53,140
It hurts.

655
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:55,060
Mother.

656
00:32:55,980 --> 00:32:57,180
