00:34:00,290 --> 00:34:01,130
My son.

673
00:34:02,180 --> 00:34:03,490
Come home with me.

674
00:34:03,490 --> 00:34:04,330
Zigui.

675
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:05,740
Come home with me.

676
00:34:06,490 --> 00:34:07,380
Come home.

677
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:18,660
Come home.

678
00:34:18,660 --> 00:34:19,500
